        <div class="faqs">
            <div class="question">
                <h3>What is sop! and what is its purpose?</h3>
                <svg width="15" height="10" viewBox="0 0 42 25">
                    <path d="M3 3L21 21L39 3" stroke="white" stroke-width="7" stroke-linecap="round" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                <p>shit osu! players (sop!) is a community based in Norway. Originally focused on the game osu!,
                    it has expanded its interests to include various other games. The purpose of sop! is to provide a
                    space for gamers to connect, make friends, and participate in community events.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

