            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                <p>To become a member of sop!, you can join our Discord server and introduce yourself to the community.
                    From there, you'll be able to participate in events and activities and become an active member of
                    the community.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faqs">
            <div class="question">
                <h3>What games does sop! focus on, besides osu!?</h3>
